#### Expected behaviour
If Erigon needs to unwind automatically it will do so and keep working.


#### Actual behaviour
Erigon tried to unwind automatically and failed, I guess. Since then it logs the same every millisecond.

#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour
I do not know, it happened on its own.

#### Backtrace
The beginning ERROR on each line with the timestamp is from the LogsExplorer, the json logs are coming from erigon.
I think the most interesting lines are around the one beginning with "ERROR 2024-12-17T18:06:58.175630096Z"
